          <ul class="dropdown-menu text-small">
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/favorite">Favorite</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/upload">Upload Art</a></li>
            <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="login">Sign out</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <form action="/product/create" method="post">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="category" class="form-label">Artwork Categories</label>
        <select class="form-select" id="category" required>
          <option value="" selected disabled>Select a category</option>
          <option value="01">Logo</option>
          <option value="02">Book Cover</option>
          <option value="03">Character</option>
          <option value="04">Photo</option>
          <option value="05">Poster</option>
          <option value="06">Digital Painting</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="artworkname" class="form-label">Artwork Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="artworkname" id="artworkname" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="description" class="form-label">Description</label>
        <textarea class="form-control" name="description" id="description" rows="3" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="image" class="form-label">Product Image</label>
        <input type="file" class="form-control" name="image" id="image" accept="image/*" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Upload</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <footer class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-5 py-5 my-5 border-top bg-dark footer-text">
        <div class="col mb-3">
            <a href="/index" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none">
                <img src="https://img2.pic.in.th/pic/Logo98c6bfecfe91ca4b.jpeg" alt="Logo" width="1000" height="auto">
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="col mb-3">

        </div>

        <div class="col mb-3">
            <h5>Categories</h5>
            <ul class="nav flex-column">
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-white">All Categories</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-white">Logo</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-white">Character</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-white">Photo</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-white">Poster</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="col mb-3">
            <h5>About Us</h5>
            <ul class="nav flex-column">
                <li class="nav-item mb-2">
                    <p>เว็บไซต์นี้สร้างขึ้นมาเพื่อส่งงานโปรเจ็ค รายวิชา 226297 เทคโนโลยีการเขียนโปรแกรมเว็บไซต์.</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="col mb-3">
            <h5>Contact Us</h5>
            <ul class="nav flex-column">
                <li class="nav-item mb-2">
                    <p><strong><i class="fas fa-envelope nav-link p-0 text-white"></i> Email:</strong> 65021633@up.ac.th</p>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item mb-2">
                    <p><strong><i class="fas fa-phone nav-link p-0 text-white"></i> Phone:</strong> 098-763-9489</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
